        "action": "Allow EU and non-EU HGV drivers to exchange their licenses for UK ones for free",
        "additional_details": "Currently the UK won't accept drivers like me with a non-UK license after 1 year of driving in the UK. Exchanging these licenses would give a good opportunity to fill those gaps in transport.",
        "background": "The Government should allow both EU and non-EU HGV driving license holders to exchange their licenses for full GB licences for free. This should help fill the UK\u2019s transport needs.",
